                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>&amp; carried out this mode<lb/> of enlisting the feelings of our<lb/> citizens\n                towards the pecuniary<lb/> aid of the people of our<lb/> sister city <add>?</add>\n                but<lb/> a very short notice was given<lb/> through the papers, but omitted<lb/> to\n                be announced on <date>Sabbath</date><lb/>\n                <sic>preceeding</sic> the discourse, which<lb/> was to be on <date>Sunday</date>,\n                &amp; which<lb/> omission &amp; short notice com<lb/>bined prevented a great<lb/>\n                number from attending<lb/> we secured one Hundred<lb/> Dolls &amp; remitted it to\n                the <add>?</add><lb/> society. Since then we have been<lb/> solicited by the\n                Benevolent Society<lb/> of <add>?</add> &amp; we have from the 2d<lb/>\n                <add>?</add> more to remit. So you<lb/> must admit that our <add>?</add><lb/> Hazan\n                &amp; Sec<add>?</add> has done some<lb/> good by his example &amp; precepts<lb/>\n                Little or but a small amt has as<lb/> yet been collected from other\n                <add>?</add><lb/> I wish you would notice them<lb/>\n                <add>?</add> above sealed in your next<lb/> Occident for altho our congregation<lb/>\n                after the <add>?</add> and dispersed circu<lb/>lary for aid to the several\n                    <placeName>North</placeName> &amp; <placeName>South</placeName><lb/> the only\n                response we ever got was your Ocd<lb/>\n                <add>?</add> candlesticks which I suppose your trustees<lb/> then, intended we\n                should con<add>?</add> them<lb/> into gold.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3ws8j648/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
